ber":"2049","dbdateline":"1432087453","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"29008337","tid":"1085129","first":"0","author":"战斗机13号","authorid":"1498","dateline":"2015-5-20 10:07","message":"这还不简单，明日香就是典型的宁为诸侯不为皇帝。跟我的为人哲学一模一样。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"2111","username":"战斗机13号","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"2050","dbdateline":"1432087646","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"29008340","tid":"1085129","first":"0","author":"66666","authorid":"3769","dateline":"2015-5-20 10:07","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=29007731&amp;ptid=1085129\"><font color=\"#999999\">米藕酱油 发表于 2015-5-20 09:19</font></a><br />\r\n从同情部长角度来说，明日香的确有诟病之处，把烦恼推给部长去直面<br />\r\n但明日香自己来说，只是贯彻了自己追求 ...</div><br />\n明日香就跟青梅竹马说的一样，根本看不懂她到底想要干什么","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"2112","username":"66666","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"2051","dbdateline":"1432087652","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"29008359","tid":"1085129","first":"0","author":"cyclotron","authorid":"180778","dateline":"2015-5-20 10:08","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=29008296&amp;ptid=1085129\"><font color=\"#999999\">lostinyume 发表于 2015-5-20 10:04</font></a><br />\r\n以明日香对音乐的热爱做成一个旁观者的姿态就已经是承受了心理压力的表现了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，似乎听他们说明日香家 ...</div><br />\n家庭问题看2064L和里面的链接，我对这个角色的综合概括见2069L<br />\r\n明日香对音乐热爱，但从她与家庭的决裂起始，她的热爱的形式就已经变成了一种孤高的姿态<br />\r\n而且也正因为她对音乐如此热爱，才让她与不那么热爱音乐的人产生了距离","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"2113","username":"cyclotron","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"2052","dbdateline":"1432087731","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"29008400","tid":"1085129","first":"0","author":"cyclotron","authorid":"180778","dateline":"2015-5-20 10:11","message":"<div class=\"rep